txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Albino fur from the beasts to the south of the outpost of Gwingris. You can return the items to Maedlathron at Gwingris in Eregion for reward.
'These furs will be used wisely. Thank you.'
'Not all beasts are lost, but there are many here that are. I require a collection of their fur.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Albino Fur
Maedlathron awaits the return of a collection of albino fur at the Elf-encampment at Gwingris.
Deliver the albino fur to Maedlathron in Gwingris within Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver albino fur from the beasts to the south of the Elf-encampment of Gwingris to the Elf Maedlathron.
Wanted: Albino fur from the beasts to the south of the outpost of Gwingris.
